However, I have a little concern regarding the following.
```
if (entry == NULL) 
{ 
    entry = NewCacheEntry();
} 
VerifyOrExit(entry != NULL, error = kThreadError_NoBufs); 
```
This part seems to be able to fail due to the following from `NewCacheEntry()`:
```
if (mCache[i].mState == Cache::kStateQuery && mCache[i].mFailures == 0) 
